column3: “It’s what I like to call Pressure, hits hard but in a nice way, great for getting baked. I’ll be nice and not give the whole 10/10 to do other strains justice...buuuut you wanna talk about FULL BODY 9.9/10 overall”
“This strain is very sweet and fruity with a hint of diesel. It has a smooth hit that leaves you coughing in the end. Very good for morning sessions and before tasks.”
“Nice earthy smell, good for day time use, 5.8/10 .. nice taste also”
